Purpose

The purpose of this document is to define the complete development environment, tools, technologies, workflows, and setup process required to build and maintain the Master Portfolio project.

This document serves as:

A project setup guide
An onboarding document
A reference for future maintenance
A reproducible development environment specification

The goal is to ensure that the project can be set up from scratch quickly and consistently on any machine.

Development Philosophy

The development environment should be:

✅ Simple

✅ Reproducible

✅ Scalable

✅ Beginner Friendly

✅ Professional

✅ Suitable for long-term maintenance

The project should follow real-world software engineering practices rather than ad-hoc development.

